{"tid":1506912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「有機會立辱警罪」2019 司政報告諮詢","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:28:39.000Z","uid":283464,"like":63,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"dc68b4105d5f4e00768e35d540b835ea323085b8","tid":1506912,"uid":283464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"2019司政報告諮詢係咪都好寫番啲正常嘢，唔好比d藍絲狗喺度亂咁寫<br />\n記住唔好寫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;唔好&quot;咩野</span></span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要寫要咩嘢</span></span> 或者取消d咩<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩好提議就直接寫落去個公眾諮詢/reply啦❨reply 左我再group❩<br />\n<br />\n一班五毛藍絲已經做緊嘢啦<br />\n例如：辱警罪 , 檬面法 等等<br />\n<br />\n不過佢有d都寫得幾好 立法會議員幾多次唔出席就取消資格<br />\n<br />\n2019公衆諮詢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.policyaddress.gov.hk/consultation19/chi/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.policyaddress.gov.hk%2Fconsultation19%2Fchi%2Fshare.php&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=97225e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.policyaddress.gov.hk/consultation19/chi/share.php</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地個傳送門❨大家可以睇睇佢地寫左d 咩❩:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/463725033650262?view=permalink&amp;id=2541491759206902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F463725033650262%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D2541491759206902&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=50a47a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/463725033650262?view=permalink&amp;id=2541491759206902</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZq7anq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZq7anq.jpg&h=7f189979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0fa1090815fa7a6fd34e96a94cf0f807d06b31cb","tid":1506912,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"adf137436f156b419d88a330d1b2a5ff5df6b8af","tid":1506912,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=caf469cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d69a553786fad930b8f869fd8261ecd77061e4ab","tid":1506912,"uid":42487,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"藍絲咪撚再講愛國<br />\n你班柒頭愛既只係共產黨<br />\n全世界都係共產黨騎劫左中國<br />\n咪撚道德綁架愛國情愫 屌你老母"},{"pid":"38428175372334b3ab743aa2e4c6a65da29b34f6","tid":1506912,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"小弟文采唔太好,有無template?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65f8c14f16ddd9166c2bfdb43cbd5495883214a","tid":1506912,"uid":40932,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"d權仲勁過特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad967c7b2759e5c322f598d99792ac1f63d3d520","tid":1506912,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:29:43.000Z","msg":"戇九，卧底都唔可以蒙面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0627259a0439244cfd14eca8a364fa529a86ae73","tid":1506912,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\